Package: TheOpenAIR
Type: Package
Title: Integrate OpenAI's Large Language Models into Your R Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ulrich", "Matter", email = "umatter@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")), person("Jonathan", "Chassot", email = "jonathan.chassot@unisg.ch", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Ulrich Matter <umatter@protonmail.com>
Description: Utilizing OpenAI's API as the backend, TheOpenAIR offers R wrapper functions for the ChatGPT endpoint and several high-level functions that enable the integration of ChatGPT's capabilities in diverse data-related tasks, such as data cleansing and automated analytics script generation.
